          "process_md": "The applicant must approach the Department of Animal Husbandry &amp; Veterinary Services,\nU.T. Administration of Daman &amp; Diu and Dadra &amp; Nagar Haveli, for availing benefits under the Establishment of Small Scale Dairy Unit (SSDU) (for 10 cows).\n<br>\n\n"
