      "schemeDefinitions": [],
      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant must be a resident of the Union Territory of Daman and Diu and Dadra and Nagar Haveli.\n1. The applicant should establish a small-scale dairy unit with 10 milch cows.\n1. The applicant should procure indigenous Gir breed cows only.\n1. The applicant should avail a bank loan for implementation of the project.\n1. The applicant should utilise the subsidy strictly for approved components.\n1. The applicant should maintain records as per the General Financial Rules, 1963.\n\n> **Preference / Reservation / Relaxation:** The applicant belonging to the Scheduled Caste or the Scheduled Tribe category is eligible for a higher subsidy rate under the back-ended subsidy and insurance components.\n\n<br>\n\n",
